		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Dwedit wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">What about the 800 pound gorilla in the room... Art?</div>
<br />Ripped graphics should definitely not be allowed, IMO.
<br />
<br />To me art  has the same problems as music. I'm a decent artist, so graphics are not a problem for me, but I suck at making music (and coding music engines), while most of you can handle it just fine. I don't even know most of the terminology.
<br />
<br />This means I'll either have to take a stab at it anyway (and accept that the result will be probably far from outstanding) or find someone competent that's willing to help me, for whatever price we agree on.
<br />
<br />In my case, I'll probably give a shot at making the music myself. Looking for help is tempting, but if I ever expect to get better I gotta try it myself sometime.

		

